		<title>08PURDYSBURN HOSPITAL</title>
		<content> Although there are several            
 buildings connected with the hospital 
 in the surrounding area, plans are    
 being made to make the hospital       
 smaller ,so the number of patients can
 be reduced.In this way the patients   
 can get more individual attention.    
 Purdysburn is a well run hospital     
 which caters for the needs of the     
 mentally ill,substance abusers and    
 the psycho-geriatric patients.        
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
